  net-perf probe|record|drift [--targets ...] [--threshold-pct N] [--json]
                               R276 (E3.M6): network performance
                               baseline + drift detection. Records
                               ping/dig/curl-TTFB metrics, persists
                               baseline as first sample per target,
                               then `drift` compares latest vs
