  SOVEREIGN_OS_LOG_LEVEL       debug|info|warn|error
  SOVEREIGN_OS_NONINTERACTIVE  set to skip all prompts (CI mode)

  M060 cross-repo mirror chain (selfdef → sovereign-os bridge, read-only):
    m060-doctor [--strict] [--json]     Smoke-check the chain (10 mirror
