                                        override the default
                                        http://localhost:9100/metrics.
    observability-status [--strict] [--json]
                                        NEW: cross-vertical triage probing
                                        ALL 6 observability verticals shipped
                                        to date (M060 + MS022 + four-watchdog
                                        + modules + daemon-process + AppArmor)
                                        in one shot via the 3 proxy daemons +
                                        node_exporter scrape. Operator-
                                        runnable single-command status across
                                        the entire observability surface.
                                        Exit 0=all green / 1=any WARN+FAIL /
                                        2=any proxy unreachable. R10212
                                        read-only — never mutates.
                                        Also: obs-status alias.
    ms022-doctor [--strict] [--json]    Triage the MS022 SSE subscriber-
                                        quota chain (proxy daemon /healthz
                                        + state classifier + envelope shape
                                        + systemd unit + master-dashboard
                                        proxy path). Exit 0/1/2 = GREEN/
                                        YELLOW/RED. R10212 read-only —
                                        every fix is an ssh-to-selfdef
                                        command, never a sovereign-os
                                        mutation. Use --strict for CI to
                                        require state=ok everywhere.
    m060-health probe|state [--json]    Daemon-side per-artifact health.
                                        `state` returns just the verdict.
    profile-mirror show [--json]        D-02 active-profile mirror
    rules-mirror snapshot|summaries [--json]
                                        D-12 nftables rules mirror
    grants-mirror snapshot [--json]     D-13 filesystem grants mirror
    capability-mirror snapshot [--json] D-14 capability-tokens mirror
    sandbox-mirror snapshot [--json]    D-15 sandbox-allocations mirror
    audit-mirror snapshot|integrity|trace <id> [--json]
                                        D-16 audit-chain mirror; `trace`
                                        looks up ONE span by trace_id with
