    quarantine-mirror snapshot [--json] D-17 quarantine mirror
    trust-mirror snapshot [--json]      D-18 trust-scores mirror
    tui-mirror snapshot|panels [--json] MS007 canonical TUI layout
    cli-mirror snapshot|summaries|mutating [--json]
