  Refresh-loop TUI surface for the R456 anti-minimization audit.
  Continuously re-renders the 8-pattern report (todo-no-anchor /
  empty-stub / skipped-no-followup / surface-gap / doc-gap /
  mandate-todo / minimize-phrase / partial-status). Operator-§1g
  standing rule: "Do not minimize or settle for less."

  Options:
    --refresh N       seconds between renders (default: 5, min: 1)
    --iterations N    cap the number of renders (default: 0 = unbounded;
                      SOVEREIGN_OS_DRY_RUN=1 forces a single render)
ANTI_MIN_WATCH_HELP
        return 0
