  surface-map watch [--refresh N] [--iterations N]

  Refresh-loop TUI surface for the R453 §1g coverage matrix.
  Continuously re-renders the module × surface coverage view across
  the 8 operator-named surfaces (core / cli / TUI / API / MCP /
  Dashboard / Web App / Service).
  Operator-§1g verbatim: "everything is not just core, not just cli,
  not just TUI, not just API, not just tool and MCP but also
  Dashboards and Web Apps and Services".

  Options:
    --refresh N       seconds between renders (default: 5, min: 1)
    --iterations N    cap the number of renders (default: 0 = unbounded;
                      SOVEREIGN_OS_DRY_RUN=1 forces a single render)
SURFACE_MAP_WATCH_HELP
        return 0
